[3] Portugal (Lisbon and Vale do Tejo region)
Date: Thu 22 Nov 2018
Source: The Portugal News [edited]
http://theportugalnews.com/news/fourteen-cases-of-measles-detected-in-lisbon-and-vale-do-tejo/47559


Fourteen cases of measles have been detected in Lisbon and Vale do Tejo.

The Health Board said the cases arose from 2 different outbreak sources, both imported from other European countries.

The DGS said all cases involve adults, one of whom has been admitted to hospital but is stable, and added no new cases are expected.

