[Kiryas Joel is a village within the town of Monroe in Orange County, New York, United States. The majority of its residents are Yiddish-speaking Hasidic Jews who belong to the worldwide Satmar Hasidic sect. There has been vaccine hesitancy in the orthodox Jewish community on the east coast of the US, and elsewhere, even though Rabbonim have urged vaccination. - Mod.LK]

